{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idd3b87d28-3a6f-11f1-8dc6-9561437cf370","identifier":"/us/usc/t11/s1231"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1231"},"text":"§ 1231.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Special tax provisions","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idd3b87d29-3a6f-11f1-8dc6-9561437cf370","identifier":"/us/usc/t11/s1231/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The issuance, transfer, or exchange of a security, or the making or delivery of an instrument of transfer under a plan confirmed under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t11/s1225"},"text":"section 1225 of this title","children":[],"tail":", may not be taxed under any law imposing a stamp tax or similar tax."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idd3b87d2a-3a6f-11f1-8dc6-9561437cf370","identifier":"/us/usc/t11/s1231/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" The court may authorize the proponent of a plan to request a determination, limited to questions of law, by any governmental unit charged with responsibility for collection or determination of a tax on or measured by income, of the tax effects, under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t11/s346"},"text":"section 346 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and under the law imposing such tax, of the plan. In the event of an actual controversy, the court may declare such effects after the earlier of—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idd3b87d2b-3a6f-11f1-8dc6-9561437cf370","identifier":"/us/usc/t11/s1231/b/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the date on which such governmental unit responds to the request under this subsection; or","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idd3b87d2c-3a6f-11f1-8dc6-9561437cf370","identifier":"/us/usc/t11/s1231/b/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" 270 days after such request.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idd3b87d2d-3a6f-11f1-8dc6-9561437cf370"},"text":"(Added and amended ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/99/554/tII/s255"},"text":"Pub. L. 99–554, title II, § 255","children":[],"tail":", title III, § 302(f), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1986-10-27"},"text":"Oct. 27, 1986","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/100/3113"},"text":"100 Stat. 3113","children":[],"tail":", 3124; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/103/65/s1"},"text":"Pub. L. 103–65, § 1","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1993-08-06"},"text":"Aug. 6, 1993","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/107/311"},"text":"107 Stat. 311","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/105/277/dC/tI/s149/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 105–277, div. C, title I, § 149(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1998-10-21"},"text":"Oct. 21, 1998","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/112/2681-610"},"text":"112 Stat. 2681–610","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/106/5/s1/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 106–5, § 1(1)","children":[],"tail":", (2), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1999-03-30"},"text":"Mar. 30, 1999","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/113/9"},"text":"113 Stat. 9","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/106/70/s1"},"text":"Pub. L. 106–70, § 1","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1999-10-09"},"text":"Oct. 9,